text: Pokok Bay, 17 miles SE of Martin Point, is about 1 mile across. Bars
label: BODY

text: extend out from both sides of the entrance. Depths are about 7 feet in
label: BODY

label: BODY

text: be approached from the W, but care must be taken to stay off the
label: BODY

text: sandbar that makes out from the NW side. The bay has good holding
label: BODY

text: bottom and good protection from ice and winds.
